frames.caption: A majestic eagle-headed warrior stands atop a rocky cliff, clad in ornate armor and holding a glowing staff. The American flag drapes from its shoulder, and the Statue of Liberty is visible in the distance, set against a dramatic sunset sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical and patriotic setting, where an eagle-headed warrior symbolizes strength and freedom. The presence of the Statue of Liberty and the American flag suggests themes of national pride and guardianship.

frames.caption: A majestic, armored eagle stands atop a rocky cliff, holding a glowing staff and draped with a tattered American flag. The scene is set against a dramatic sky with the Statue of Liberty visible in the distance. The eagle exudes power and vigilance, symbolizing strength and freedom.
frames.description: The scene depicts a powerful, anthropomorphic eagle warrior standing on a rocky outcrop. The setting is a dramatic, post-apocalyptic landscape with a glowing sky, and the Statue of Liberty in the background, suggesting themes of resilience and patriotism.
